.TH wxGridBagSizer 3 "wx 2.5.4" "Ericsson AB" "Erlang Module Definition"
.SH NAME
wxGridBagSizer \- A \fIwxSizer\fR that can lay out items in a virtual grid like a \fIwxFlexGridSizer\fR but in this case explicit positioning of the items is allowed using \fIwxGBPosition\fR (not implemented in wx), and items can optionally span more than one row and/or column using \fIwxGBSpan\fR (not implemented in wx).

.SH DESCRIPTION
.PP
This class is derived, and can use functions, from:


